Package com.mzaart.aquery.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    IllegalParentException
    Signals that a View's parent isn't a View
    IllegalViewActionException
    Signals that an illegal action is requested from a View.
    SDKVersionException
    Signals that a method that is not supported by the current SDK version is called
    ViewNotFoundException
    Signals that an AQuery object is being constructed from an ID that doesn't correspond to any view.
